_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final attempt\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"the trio\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"their place\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A team of 13 swimmers, includingDaniel WiffenandMona McSharrywho have already achieved Olympic qualification, will also be competing.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A team\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"13 swimmers\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"includingDaniel WiffenandMona McSharrywho\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic qualification\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ellen Walshe, who has opted not to compete in Doha, is also qualified.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Walshe\", \"score\": 0.9999979159039302, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellen Walshe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Walshe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellen_Walshe\"}, {\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.287373266966178e-14, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the swimmers, the championships in Doha is the penultimate occasion to secure qualification times before a final Olympic trials in Dublin in May.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.287373266966